WEBVTT

00:00:28.771 --> 00:00:33.529
(Laughter)

00:00:33.553 --> 00:00:36.331
I couldn't even do the simplest trick,

00:00:36.355 --> 00:00:38.672
but it was very natural for me,

00:00:38.696 --> 00:00:42.664
because I was not dextrous,
and hated all sports.

00:00:43.561 --> 00:00:46.298
But after one week of practicing,

00:00:46.322 --> 00:00:48.715
my throws became more like this:

00:00:54.585 --> 00:00:55.735
A bit better.

00:00:56.834 --> 00:01:00.744
I thought, the yo-yo
is something for me to be good at.